00:30:29,450 --> 00:30:31,310
They're formally charging
Donna's father,

781
00:30:31,320 --> 00:30:33,619
and we need to figure out a way
to get his case thrown out.

782
00:30:33,620 --> 00:30:35,380
Well, then we have to get
my case thrown out,

783
00:30:35,390 --> 00:30:37,820
because then they won't care
about Donna's dad.

784
00:30:37,830 --> 00:30:39,199
