00:30:39,200 --> 00:30:40,559
I went to see Gerard.

786
00:30:40,560 --> 00:30:42,190
God damn it, didn't I
tell you not to do that?

787
00:30:42,200 --> 00:30:43,840
That was before we knew
he wasn't the one

788
00:30:43,841 --> 00:30:45,160
that tipped them off.

