00:33:09,521 --> 00:33:11,940
Please.

858
00:33:11,950 --> 00:33:14,849
You think I don't know this
letter is complete bullshit?

859
00:33:14,850 --> 00:33:16,310
I pull this clown
up on the stand,

860
00:33:16,320 --> 00:33:17,889
he's gonna tell me
the truth in a minute.

861
00:33:17,890 --> 00:33:19,459
Okay,
this clown is one of

862
00:33:19,460 --> 00:33:22,229
the most distinguished ethics
professors in the country.

