to shreds.

883
00:34:08,340 --> 00:34:12,179
Your Honor, Ms. Gibbs and I
have come to an agreement.

884
00:34:12,180 --> 00:34:14,809
She's dropping all charges
against James Paulsen,

885
00:34:14,810 --> 00:34:17,010
and we withdraw
our motion to dismiss.

886
00:34:21,020 --> 00:34:23,859
See you next week.

