00:34:27,930 --> 00:34:30,259
Unfortunately,
neither am I.

891
00:34:30,260 --> 00:34:31,590
Harvey Specter.

892
00:34:31,600 --> 00:34:32,959
Jim Paulsen.

893
00:34:32,960 --> 00:34:34,520
I assume this is
about the opportunity

